                    <ul>
                        <li>FIEcho by CGP, IMA a comprehensive clinical oriented certificate programme in Echocardiography</li>
                        <li>DFID – by CMC Vellore in Diabetes management</li>
                    </ul>
                    <h3>Work Experience:</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Tutor in Community Medicine at PSG IMSR Coimbatore – 2002 to 2004</li>
                        <li>Insurance Medical Officer at ESIC Model Hospital, Kollam – 2004 to 2006</li>
                        <li>Assistant Surgeon at Govt PHC Kudimangalam – 2006 to 2009</li>
                        <li>Consultant Physician at Govt Hospital Palladam – 2013 to 2015</li>
                        <li>Currently Senior Consultant Physician at S V Clinic Palladam</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <hr>

